source/France\"}, {\"begin\": 356, \"end\": 361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 1.0570515463220944e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 437, \"end\": 443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9802535631707903, \"rank\": 0.013617213066516897, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ken Browne\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 215}, {\"ngram\": \"Copied WATCH\", \"from\": 225, \"to\": 237}, {\"ngram\": \"Ken Browne\", \"from\": 239, \"to\": 249}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 289, \"to\": 301}, {\"ngram\": \"At least 15 million people\", \"from\": 302, \"to\": 328}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 366, \"to\": 378}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 392, \"to\": 400}, {\"ngram\": \"the largest rollout\", \"from\": 411, \"to\": 430}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 460, \"to\": 467}]}, {\"sentence\": \"S\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cecurity will involve 45,000 police and gendarmes, 20,000 soldiers and 15-20,000 private security personnel.\", \"from\": 473, \"to\": 584, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"S\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cecurity\", \"from\": 473, \"to\": 484}, {\"ngram\": \"45,000 police\", \"from\": 498, \"to\": 511}, {\"ngram\": \"gendarmes\", \"from\": 516, \"to\": 525}, {\"ngram\": \"20,000 soldiers\", \"from\": 527, \"to\": 542}, {\"ngram\": \"15-20,000 private security personnel\", \"from\": 547, \"to\": 583}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition, around 100,000 active agents will try to keep Paris safe during the world's largest sporting event.\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 697, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 644, \"end\": 649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 1.0570515463220944e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 588, \"to\": 596}, {\"ngram\": \"around 100,000 active agents\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 626}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's largest sporting event\", \"from\": 662, \"to\": 696}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cGuillaume Fard\\u00c3\\u00a9, Security Expert, Sciences Po Paris, said: \\\"There are three main threats.\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 792, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cGuillaume\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 711}, {\"ngram\": \"Fard\\u00c3\\u00a9\", \"from\": 712, \"to\": 718}, {\"ngram\": \"Security Expert\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 735}, {\"ngram\": \"Sciences Po Paris\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 754}, {\"ngram\": \"three main threats\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 791}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is a so-called protest threat, there is a threat that is more closely linked to crime, to delinquency.\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 901, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a so-called protest threat\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 828}, {\"ngram\": \"a threat\", \"from\": 839, \"to\": 847}, {\"ngram\": \"crime\", \"from\": 879, \"to\": 884}, {\"ngram\": \"delinquency\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 900}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And then there is the issue of terrorism.\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 943, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the issue\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 929}, {\"ngram\": \"terrorism\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 942}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Imagine a mass terrorist attack, that's the worst-case scenario.\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 1010, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a mass terrorist attack\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 977}, {\"ngram\": \"the worst-case scenario\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 1009}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the President of the Republic's bet is that there is no success without some risk, then mitigating that risk with the commitment of 100 percent of our resources.\\\"\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1177, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the President\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1028}, {\"ngram\": \"the Republic's bet\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1050}, {\"ngram\": \"no success\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1078}, {\"ngram\": \"some risk\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1096}, {\"ngram\": \"that risk\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1123}, {\"ngram\": \"the commitment\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1143}, {\"ngram\": \"100 percent\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1158}, {\"ngram\": \"our resources\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1175}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Patrolling near the Eiffel Tower with the Games starting July 26.\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1244, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1211}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1226}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/Gonzalo Fuentes/Reuters 'Protective bubbles' will be set up around sensitive events, including a heavy police presence on the ground and Permanent Airborne Security Systems in the sky.\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1431, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Fuentes/Reuters 'Protective bubbles\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1289}, {\"ngram\": \"sensitive events\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1329}, {\"ngram\": \"a heavy police presence\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1364}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 1368, \"to\": 1378}, {\"ngram\": \"Permanent Airborne Security Systems\", \"from\": 1383, \"to\": 1418}, {\"ngram\": \"the sky\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1429}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This will have helicopters and drones, while jammer-gun operators will be ready to neutralize malicious drone attacks by cutting their communications.\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1583, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"helicopters\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1459}, {\"ngram\": \"drones\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1470}, {\"ngram\": \"jammer-gun operators\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1498}, {\"ngram\": \"malicious drone attacks\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1550}, {\"ngram\": \"their communications\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1582}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cParis 2024 is France's first Olympics in a hundred years and 2,000 police reinforcements are coming from partner countries around the world.\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1728, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1602, \"end\": 1608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9491082433450465, \"rank\": 0.04394092559742886, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a hundred years\", \"from\": 1629, \"to\": 1644}, {\"ngram\": \"2,000 police reinforcements\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1676}, {\"ngram\": \"partner countries\", \"from\": 1693, \"to\": 1710}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1718, \"to\": 1727}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Spain alone is sending almost 200 officers.\", \"from\": 1729, \"to\": 1772, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1729, \"end\": 1734, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"score\": 0.8769431130418636, \"rank\": 0.0743650878985105, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"almost 200 officers\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1771}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cThen there are the QR codes that locals have to download just to move around the city and get home, while many streets and bridges have also been closed causing traffic gridlock.\", \"from\": 1774, \"to\": 1955, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the QR codes\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1804}, {\"ngram\": \"locals\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1816}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\"